## Third-party components

This project orchestrates several third-party software components,
each distributed under its own license. **This repository neither
redistributes nor wraps any of their binaries** — every component is
either installed through its upstream distribution channel (Homebrew
cask, GitHub Releases, upstream CDN) or downloaded at setup time
from the vendor. No third-party source is vendored into the repo
tree either; see `.gitignore` (which excludes `vendor/` and any
`*.dll` / `*.exe` / `*.so` / `.wine-*`).

Runtime dependencies:

- **Wine (stable)** — LGPL-2.1-or-later.
  https://www.winehq.org/
  Installed via Homebrew Cask `wine-stable` (Gcenx build). The
  optional `-fvisibility=default` rebuild clones upstream Wine
  source from https://gitlab.winehq.org/wine/wine at tag
  `wine-11.0`, builds it locally, and copies only
  `dlls/winemac.drv/winemac.so` over the Homebrew cask. The
  original `winemac.so` is preserved as
  `winemac.so.gcenx-backup`.
- **Winetricks** — LGPL-2.1-or-later.
  https://github.com/Winetricks/winetricks
- **DXMT** — MIT License (Copyright (c) 2023 Feifan He).
  https://github.com/3Shain/dxmt
  `scripts/04-install-dxmt.sh` fetches an official release tarball.
  `scripts/07-build-dxmt-fork.sh` builds the fork branch
  `notpop/dxmt@debug/present-path-tracing` from source.
- **GStreamer runtime** — LGPL-2.1.
  https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/
- **Steam client** (installed on demand by the end user) — subject
  to the Steam Subscriber Agreement.
  https://store.steampowered.com/subscriber_agreement/
  Fetched from the official Valve CDN at runtime.

Build-time dependencies (only invoked when compiling from source):

- **Homebrew** — BSD-2-Clause.
  https://brew.sh/
- **mingw-w64 toolchain** — runtime is public domain / MIT-like;
  build tools are GPL. https://www.mingw-w64.org/
  Only used to cross-compile `wrapper/steamwebhelper.exe`. The
  resulting binary is not tracked in this repository.
- **LLVM 15** — Apache License 2.0 with LLVM Exceptions.
  https://llvm.org/
  Self-built by `scripts/07-build-dxmt-fork.sh` as an x86_64 LLVM
  needed by the DXMT shader compiler.
- **3Shain Wine tarball** (`v8.16-3shain`) — LGPL-2.1-or-later
  (inherited from Wine). https://github.com/3Shain/wine
  Downloaded as a link-time input for the DXMT build.
- **Meson, Ninja, CMake, Bison, Flex, gettext, pkg-config,
  freetype** — each under its own upstream license. Fetched via
  Homebrew at install time.

No secrets, no tokens, no game binaries, and no personal data are
committed to this repository.
